Gamers don’t have to spend hundreds of rand to play some of the best and most popular titles on the market. Subscription services like EA’s Origin Access and Microsoft’s Game Pass have made gaming more affordable, with monthly fees from as little as R48.50 providing access to large libraries of popular games. However, for those unable or unwilling to spend this amount, several great titles are available to download and play for free. Below is a selection of the best free-to-play games to jump into during the lockdown. Call of Duty: Warzone is a battle royale FPS which borrows elements from several other games of its kind to deliver an experience unlike any of them. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-347207" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warzone-640x430.jpg" alt="Warzone" width="640" height="430" /> Dauntless is a co-op monster hunter RPG in which you can play solo or join a team of up to three players. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-348389" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Dauntless.jpg" alt="Dauntless" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Dauntless.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Dauntless-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Dauntless-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Destiny 2 is an action-packed sci-fi FPS from Halo creator Bungie. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-348397" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Destiny-2.jpg" alt="Destiny 2" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Destiny-2.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Destiny-2-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Destiny-2-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The fast-paced battle royale from Titanfall creators Respawn came out of nowhere when it was released on 4 February 2019 without any prior marketing or announcements. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-347205" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apex-Legends-640x430.jpg" alt="Apex Legends" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apex-Legends.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apex-Legends-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Apex-Legends-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The original Defence of the Ancients (DOTA) was an incredibly popular mod for real-time strategy game Warcraft III. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-348383" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/DOTA-2.jpg" alt="DOTA 2" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/DOTA-2.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/DOTA-2-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/DOTA-2-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> In this third-person sci-fi action shooter, you play as one of the Tenno, alien warriors who are masters of blade and gun combat. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-348381" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warframe.jpg" alt="Warframe" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warframe.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Warframe-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/